tests.name: CN Status validation in Direct Un delivery flow Burger King

steps.context: Expect Order Status to be softdata_upload.Actual status is softdata_upload
Expect Order Status to be assigned_for_delivery.Actual status is assigned_for_delivery
Burger king - Start Bike
Expect Order Status to be startbike.Actual status is startbike
Burger king - Reached Destination
Expect Order Status to be reachedgate.Actual status is reachedgate
Burger king - Swipe on Undelivery
Selecting Un delivered reasn - Un delivered Screen
Undelivery Reason Page - Confirm
Expect Order Status to be attempted.Actual status is attempted
Order Details page- Return to Store
Rider Actions Page - Ready For Order
Expect Ready For Order Text

Expect Order Status to be reachedgate.Actual status is reachedgate

Expect Order Status to be reachedgate.Actual status is reachedgate
Burger king - Swipe on Delivery
Add payment Page - Add Button
Expect Order Status to be delivered.Actual status is delivered
Order Details page- Return to Store
Rider Actions Page - Ready For Order
Expect Ready For Order Text
